content: According to the search results [[1](https://www.sportingnews.com/us/soccer/news/who-won-2022-fifa-world-cup-final-score-result-highlights-qatar/aar5gfviuuapvkmcq3tf7dep)], Argentina won the FIFA World Cup 2022 by defeating France in the final. The match took place in Qatar on December 18, 2022, and Lionel Messi scored the winning goal in the 23rd minute of the game. It's worth noting that my knowledge cutoff was in September 2021, so this information wasn't available to me at the time.
